      <p>All text read by <a href="http://chigby.org">Cameron Higby-Naquin</a>.</p>
      <p>Site artwork and symbols by <a href="http://monsterism.tumblr.com/">Marcelo Gallegos</a>.</p>
      <p>Contact me!  Requests, critiques, suggestions, sonnets, sestinas, triolets, rondels, limericks, <i>etc</i>.
        <ul>
          <li><a href="mailto:<%= @site.config[:author_email] %>">Email</a></li>
          <li><a href="http://twitter.com/<%= @site.config[:author_twitter] %>">Twitter</a></li>
          <li><%= link_to('Google+', @site.config[:author_gplus]) %></li>
          <li><%= link_to('Soundcloud', @site.config[:soundcloud_url]) %></li>
        </ul>
      </p>
